&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Build&amp;nbsp;an understanding of the Restoring Promise approach, the&amp;nbsp;Designed for&amp;nbsp;Dignity project, and prison culture change within state&amp;nbsp;corrections departments.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;469777462&amp;quot;:[720],&amp;quot;469777927&amp;quot;:[0],&amp;quot;469777928&amp;quot;:[8]}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Gain hands-on experience with designing technical&amp;nbsp;assistance&amp;nbsp;tools and activities in thoughtful and strategic ways.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;469777462&amp;quot;:[720],&amp;quot;469777927&amp;quot;:[0],&amp;quot;469777928&amp;quot;:[8]}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Support the team in delivering strategic technical&amp;nbsp;assistance&amp;nbsp;to state departments of corrections&amp;nbsp;as they&amp;nbsp;engage in&amp;nbsp;policy change, training change, and&amp;nbsp;related&amp;nbsp;research&amp;nbsp;activities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;469777462&amp;quot;:[720],&amp;quot;469777927&amp;quot;:[0],&amp;quot;469777928&amp;quot;:[8]}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
